#. <section class="sutta" id="an8.85"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an8.85:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 8"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 8"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.85:0.2"
msgid "9. Sativagga"
msgstr "9. Mindfulness"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 85. Samaṇasutta → tathāgatādhivacanasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an8.85:0.3"
msgid "85. Samaṇasutta"
msgstr "85. Terms for the Realized One"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.340"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an8.85:1.1"
msgid ""
"“‘Samaṇo’ti, bhikkhave, tathāgatassetaṃ adhivacanaṃ arahato "
"sammāsambuddhassa."
msgstr ""
"“‘Ascetic’ is a term for the Realized One, the perfected one, the fully "
"awakened Buddha."

msgctxt "an8.85:1.2"
msgid ""
"‘Brāhmaṇo’ti, bhikkhave, tathāgatassetaṃ adhivacanaṃ arahato "
"sammāsambuddhassa."
msgstr "‘Brahmin’,"

msgctxt "an8.85:1.3"
msgid ""
"‘Vedagū’ti, bhikkhave, tathāgatassetaṃ adhivacanaṃ arahato sammāsambuddhassa."
msgstr "‘Knowledge Master’,"

# See BB’s note on sequence.
msgctxt "an8.85:1.4"
msgid ""
"‘Bhisakko’ti, bhikkhave, tathāgatassetaṃ adhivacanaṃ arahato "
"sammāsambuddhassa."
msgstr "‘Healer’,"

msgctxt "an8.85:1.5"
msgid ""
"‘Nimmalo’ti, bhikkhave, tathāgatassetaṃ adhivacanaṃ arahato "
"sammāsambuddhassa."
msgstr "‘Unstained’,"

msgctxt "an8.85:1.6"
msgid ""
"‘Vimalo’ti, bhikkhave, tathāgatassetaṃ adhivacanaṃ arahato sammāsambuddhassa."
msgstr "‘Stainless’,"

msgctxt "an8.85:1.7"
msgid ""
"‘Ñāṇī’ti, bhikkhave, tathāgatassetaṃ adhivacanaṃ arahato sammāsambuddhassa."
msgstr "‘Knower’,"

msgctxt "an8.85:1.8"
msgid ""
"‘Vimutto’ti, bhikkhave, tathāgatassetaṃ adhivacanaṃ arahato "
"sammāsambuddhassāti."
msgstr ""
"and ‘Freed’ are terms for the Realized One, the perfected one, the fully "
"awakened Buddha."

# See BB’s note on the difficulties in this verse. I have nothing to add!
#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an8.85:2.1"
msgid "Yaṃ samaṇena pattabbaṃ,"
msgstr "The supreme should be attained by an ascetic,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.85:2.2"
msgid "brāhmaṇena vusīmatā;"
msgstr "a brahmin who has lived the life;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.85:2.3"
msgid "Yaṃ vedagunā pattabbaṃ,"
msgstr "it should be attained by a knowledge master,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.85:2.4"
msgid "bhisakkena anuttaraṃ."
msgstr "a healer."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an8.85:3.1"
msgid "Yaṃ nimmalena pattabbaṃ,"
msgstr "The supreme should be attained by the unstained,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.85:3.2"
msgid "vimalena sucīmatā;"
msgstr "stainless and pure;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.85:3.3"
msgid "Yaṃ ñāṇinā ca pattabbaṃ,"
msgstr "it should be attained by a knower,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.85:3.4"
msgid "vimuttena anuttaraṃ."
msgstr "who is free."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an8.85:4.1"
msgid "Sohaṃ vijitasaṅgāmo,"
msgstr "I am victorious in battle!"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.85:4.2"
msgid "mutto mocemi bandhanā;"
msgstr "Released, I release others from their chains."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.85:4.3"
msgid "Nāgomhi paramadanto,"
msgstr "I am a dragon completely tamed,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.85:4.4"
msgid "asekho parinibbuto”ti."
msgstr "an adept, I am extinguished.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.85:4.5"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
